,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d野可唔可以炒先，個價升唔升，回報幾多呀</blockquote><br />\n其實唔可以咁睇喎，就算係科技都要揾到錢先會普及<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係科學家同工程師最大分別，工程師係將科技科學融入生活，而生活就一定講到錢"},{"pid":"b6fdb491e81fd2015b85f53a462ea4fc3175aa62","tid":389993,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:07:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>GOOGLE GLASS係咪已經死左唔會出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港眼鏡舖有得賣"},{"pid":"b97d21c494c384b58053823500ea274da9c58eae","tid":389993,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:13:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>GOOGLE GLASS係咪已經死左唔會出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港眼鏡舖有得賣</blockquote><br />\n唔係<br />\n因為爆出私隱疑慮　所以低調處理<br />\n留返美國企業用"},{"pid":"9385439e30f3495aa514ef55dfdca1d21ecee530","tid":389993,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:40:31.000Z","msg":"Mycar一見就諗起Gwiz <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起gwiz 就諗起top gear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8faca07ac618574db2c9a566a6f0ab7abbd2fd","tid":389993,"uid":43510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:26:54.000Z","msg":"仲有磁能尿袋"},{"pid":"dddac2519849b856643b27ffb2a5e007d348920a","tid":389993,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:29:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有磁能尿袋</blockquote><br />\n上咗Kickstarter未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}